 Package : icecast
 Date    : April 9, 2013
 Affected: Business Server 1.0
 _______________________________________________________________________

 Problem Description:

 Updated icecast package fixes security vulnerability:
 
 Icecast didn&#039;t strip newlines from log entries, therefore allowing
 users to forge log entries (CVE-2011-4612)
 _______________________________________________________________________

 References:

 http://cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=CVE-2011-4612
 https://wiki.mageia.org/en/Support/Advisories/MGASA-2012-0211
